name: 甜花
text:
すみません……！
人形焼き──
trans: Excuse me......! Could we get some doll cakes──

name: 甘奈
text: 一袋にして、ふたりでシェアしよ～！
trans: Let's get one bag and share it～!

name: 甘奈
text:
わーっ！
無理しないで持って帰ろ？　ね？
trans: Ahhh! We can just take it home, okay?

name: 甜花
text:
にへへ……
虹色の、かき氷……

name: 甜花
text:
夢で見たやつと……
そっくり……！
trans: It's exactly like... the one in Tenka's dream......!

name: 甘奈
text: 売り切れてなくてよかったよね☆
trans: I'm glad they weren't sold out☆

name: 甘奈
text:
あ～っ……！　食べるのがもったいないけど、
溶けちゃうのももったいない～っ
trans:
Awww......! It's such a waste to eat it, but waiting for
it to melt is a waste too～

name: 甜花
text:
これ……食べたら
舌、虹色になっちゃう……？
trans:
If we...... eat this... won't our tongues... turn rainbow
too......?

name: 甘奈
text:
甜花ちゃん、先に食べてみない？
それで、甘奈が写真撮ってあげる！
trans:
Tenka-chan, wanna eat some first? And then I'll take
a picture!

name: 甘奈
text:
大丈夫だよ～
甜花ちゃん、舌が虹色になってもかわいーもん☆
trans:
Don't worry about it～ You're gonna be so cute with
that rainbow tongue☆

name: 甜花
text:
や、やってみる、ね……！
にへへ……！
trans: T-Tenka's gonna... give it a try......! Nihehe......!

name: 甘奈
text:
ね～
夕飯、ちゃんと入りそう？
trans: Right～? Think you saved enough room for dinner?

name: 甜花
text:
大丈夫……！
ちゃんとスペース、残してる……！
trans: No problem......! Tenka's got enough space......!

name: 甘奈
text:
さすが甜花ちゃん！
偉いよ～っ☆
trans: Knew I could count on you! Good girl～☆

name: 甜花
text:
にへへ……
ママと約束……したから……
trans: Nihehe...... Tenka made a promise...... with mama......

name: 甘奈
text:
甜花ちゃん、
もう食べ損ねたものとかない？
trans: Anything else you wanted to try out, Tenka-chan?

name: 甜花
text:
これ以上は……
スペース……なくなっちゃう……
trans:
But...... anything else... and... Tenka won't have enough
space......

name: 甜花
trans: Could we... go the long way......?

name: 甘奈
trans: I was thinking the exact same thing☆

name: 甘奈
text:
きっと、遠回りした方が
人通りも少ないし──
trans: There'll be less people on that route too──

name: 甘奈
text:
うんっ
……って、さっきもこれ、話さなかったっけ？
trans: Yeah. ......Wait, didn't we already say that earlier?
